      "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nAlso note that the commit comment says \"lfs rmdir\", but the actual command is \"lfs rm_entry\".  I'm personally not against \"lfs rmdir\" if it explains in the usage and man page (which is also missing from this patch) what it is supposed to be doing, but it can be either.",
